                    <span>I thought that Slave was a very good read, because I enjoyed it and couldn't put it down, which to me makes a good book. I would recommend this book to anyone, it is the compelling story of a girls struggle to survive in a world of modern day slavery, being deprived of seeing her family for 8 years eventually overcoming the abuse and humiliation of being regarded as dirty, and diseased. Beaten and starved, Mende Nazer makes her escape, and tells her brave tale.</span>
                  
              
